Program: The Documentary
Title: Episode 2
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00d43dr
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 30 Jan 2011
What sort of relationships do photographers form with the people that are the subject of their pictures? The bond can be an emotional one because the theme is often highly charged. In this BBC World Service documentary series, two photographers reveal their stories - one of hope and grief, and the other a tale of racial tension. Show less